      <title>特朗普暗示他可能不会参加 ABC 新闻与哈里斯的辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-suggests-he-might-not-attend-abc-news-debate-with-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普再次怀疑他是否会参加与民主党候选人卡马拉·哈里斯之间唯一商定的辩论，该辩论定于两周后举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-suggests-he-might-not-attend-abc-news-debate-with-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:52:28 GMT</pubDate>
